luded), and then send a request through GET or POST (including byte[] parameters) in the following way: https://open-api.alibaba.com/rest{api_path}? {query}。 As: </p><div class=\"ql-code-block-container\" spellcheck=\"false\"><select class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"><option value=\"plain\">Plain</option><option value=\"bash\">Bash</option><option value=\"cpp\">C++</option><option value=\"cs\">C#</option><option value=\"css\">CSS</option><option value=\"diff\">Diff</option><option value=\"xml\">HTML/XML</option><option value=\"java\">Java</option><option value=\"javascript\">Javascript</option><option value=\"markdown\">Markdown</option><option value=\"php\">PHP</option><option value=\"python\">Python</option><option value=\"ruby\">Ruby</option><option value=\"sql\">SQL</option></select><div class=\"ql-code-block\" data-language=\"plain\">http://open-api.alibaba.com/rest/auth/token/create?app_key=12345678&amp;code=3_500102_JxZ05Ux3cnnSSUm6dCxYg6Q26&amp;timestamp=1517820392000&amp;sign_method=sha256&amp;simplify=true&amp;sign=0B409A354C6FB222EE2C8095002ACDB2D30566151D1A2361AEE7D2627B9BCBEA</div></div><p><br></p><p><strong>Precautions  </strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>All request and response data are encoded in utf-8 format, and all parameter names and parameter values in the URL should be encoded in URL. If the Content-Type of the request is application/x-www-form-urlencoded, all parameter values in the HTTP body are also URL-encoded. If the format is multipart/form-data, the parameter values of each form field do not need to be encoded, but the charset part of each form field needs to be specified as UTF-8.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>If the URL length of the parameter name and parameter value is less than 1024 characters, you can use GET to initiate a request. If the parameter type contains byte[] or the assembled request URL is too long, you must use POST to initiate the request. All APIs can initiate requests with POST.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Signing</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">is</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">only</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">required</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">for</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">API</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">calls</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> that </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">are</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">not</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">made</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">using</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">official</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">SDK</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> of </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">international</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">site,</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">and</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">if</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">official</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">SDK</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> of </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">international</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">site</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">is</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">used,</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">this</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">step</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> of </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">SDK</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">will</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">be</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">completed</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">automatically.</span></li></ol>",
